snippet.title: Bullets Are Fatal! - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Bullets Are Fatal! is a 2.5D twin-stick fast-paced action platformer in a wild western theme. Gun your way through bandits & gunslingers, ricochet bullets and perform all kinds of trick shots to best your opponents through increasingly difficult levels or against your friends in hectic multiplayer!

Wishlist on Steam now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1385580/Bullets_Are_Fatal/
